{"tid":187934,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"木村拓哉傳進軍好萊塢 有望演出《星戰9》","createTime":"2017-04-05T10:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T23:32:41.000Z","uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71b16ef5a7a64a4b1bfdf991a090ad47293740ec","tid":187934,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"日本組合SMAP去年在出道25周年解散收場，有消息指除木村拓哉外，其餘四子決定今年不會續約尊尼事務所，只得木村留低，並獲更改合約兼任公司高層。木村單飛後的事業實在令人關注，近日有傳他計劃進軍荷李活，更秘密試鏡爭演2019年上映的《星球大戰》（Star Wars）第9集，或有可能是他繼王家衛作品《2046》及陳英雄執導的《I Come with the Rain》後，第三套接拍的海外電影。<br />\n<br />\n《星戰》第8集《星球大戰：最後絕地武士》（Star Wars：The Last Jedi）安排在今年12月上映，除了集中交代「天行者Luke」麥克咸美（Mark Hamill）跟女主角「Rey」黛絲烈尼（Daisy Ridley）之關係外，亦是「莉亞公主」嘉莉費莎（Carrie Fisher）的遺作。而暫定兩年後公開的第9集，迪士尼方面正開始籌備拍攝。有日本傳媒爆料指，木村拓哉原來已獲邀到美國試鏡，雖然片商對故事內容十分保密，但估計其爭演的角色是個精通拳法的賢者，未知角色是否擁有原力的絕地武士，若木村成功過關，他便是繼《俠盜一號：星球大戰外傳》（Rogue One: A Star Wars Story）中的甄子丹和姜文後，再有亞洲演員擔任重要角色。<br />\n<br />\n木村主演的古裝電影《無限之住人》將於本月底在日本開畫，早前有傳他與家人計劃移居海外，懷疑此舉是為了鋪路進軍荷李活。報道又指，木村在《星戰》第9集的角色都算重要，酬勞至少達3億日圓（約2,070萬港元），同時會支付他在拍攝期間的生活費，獲得巨星級待遇。不過，甄子丹接拍《俠盜一號》時一度盛傳片酬遠勝同片拍檔，其實女主角菲莉絲迪鍾斯（Felicity Jones）才是全片最高身價演員。"},{"pid":"485fa933fcd6926f9ee186bb98797c659f29dcef","tid":187934,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:43:31.000Z","msg":"亞洲人拍星戰可以好似甄子丹咁搶鏡<br />\n亦都可以好似呢幾個咁完全唔知做乜鳩<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w7hay50g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw7hay50g&h=78bd2b84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72702eec9798ede01dcee3e91ad1422bfaf5ddf5","tid":187934,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />木村<br />\n有望出hottoys"},{"pid":"0a12fa1431ea26f8c396999d4899e7f462565f3f","tid":187934,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:17:01.000Z","msg":"Starwar已經勁到完全唔驚票房毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a404a2766c246b85592fe595314e6ac9385557","tid":187934,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"係, 仲傾緊"},{"pid":"25e2998c746b5d82700381fc198db0d131939543","tid":187934,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係, 仲傾緊</blockquote><br />\n傾成點"},{"pid":"00aff9bf5856700d9ce6f28019dd65923352faf7","tid":187934,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4534553863b4cdf19cc6e9f5f20652329727a191","tid":187934,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c02304574ba109cf6a73d151689fca81cc162bd","tid":187934,"uid":50020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Starwar已經勁到完全唔驚票房毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有一大班死忠同一班潮流追捧人應該唔驚"},{"pid":"567fd73d6ec2883e67e8f2d50ca840264a560ab9","tid":187934,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T23:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你好"}]}